messages.msgSnippet: Yes Karin we are here in Tucson and you are more than welcome to come visit. I also belong to Sonoran Desert Homeschoolers that has a park meeting on Tuesdays
messages.messageBody:
Yes Karin we are here in Tucson and you are more than welcome to come visit.
I also belong to Sonoran Desert Homeschoolers that has a park meeting on
Tuesdays at Ft. Lowell Park so if you come maybe you could come that day and
meet the rest of us on this list from Tucson, who attend that meeting.

Dawn

>>Where in AZ Mary?>>

Phoenix, and wherever else Karin wants to take me. :o)

~Mary >>

Maybe a trip down to Tucson would be in order!

You are in Tucson, right Dawn?

Karin

in Phoenix
